1 (3) To the extent that the unit value of centrally assessed property includes intangible personal
2 property, that value must be removed from the unit value.
3 (b) The term does not include property used as an integral part of:
4 (i) the operation of a business; or
5 (ii) an operating unit of centrally assessed property."
6
7 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Effective date. [This act] is effective January 1, 2026.
8
9 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Applicability. [This act] applies to tax years beginning after December
10 31, 2025.
